articles.author: Tara Subramaniam, Angus Watson, Akanksha Sharma
articles.title: Sumatra, Indonesia boat: Missing Australian surfers found in water off Nias island - CNN
articles.description: Four Australian surfers who went missing after their boat was struck by a storm in a remote part of Indonesia have been rescued after more than 38 hours at sea, according to parents of the missing tourists.
